This is a collection of quotes that I used for my randomly-generated email signature for around 10 years, before most of my mail usage became web-based. A lot of them are song lyrics I like, IM quotes, video game quotes, etc. Many of them are unsourced (I&rsquo;ll correct that someday).
 I delight in my pain, and I'm shattered like your promises;
Though I try to be sane, I'm just shattered like, shattered like your promises&hellip;

&ldquo;Okay, here&rsquo;s the scenario. You are a crew member on a starship.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Cool.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Space travel is slow, you&rsquo;ll be stuck with your crewmates a long time.&rdquo;
&ldquo;So we must get along.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Yes. Communicate, listen, share limited resources.&rdquo;
&ldquo;I can do that. What&rsquo;s the starship called?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Earth.&rdquo;
